epi-NXA-aq.def: The NOX growth rate is calculated as the average annual rate of increase or decrease in NOX over the years 2005–2014. It is then adjusted for economic trends to isolate change due to policy rather than economic fluctuation.
epi-NXA-aq.name: NOx intensity trend

epi-SDA-aq.def: The SO2growth rate is calculated as the average annual rate of increase or decrease in SO2 over the years 2005–2014. It is then adjusted for economic trends to isolate change due to policy rather than economic fluctuation.
epi-SDA-aq.name: SO2 intensity trend
